    "en": "He said: Abu al-Hasan Ali ibn al-Hasan al-Maraghi reported to me, saying: Abu al-Qasim al-Hasan ibn Ali ibn al-Hasan al-Kufi narrated to us, saying: Ja'far ibn Muhammad ibn Marwan narrated to us, saying: My father narrated to us, saying: Ahmad ibn Isa narrated to us, saying: Muhammad ibn Ja'far ibn Muhammad ibn Ali narrated to us, from his father (peace be upon them all), who said:",
